--- Server Configuration ---

PORT=8080

For local dev with docker-compose, this is not needed as it's set in the compose file.

For production, this must be set.

REDIS_URL=redis://your-production-redis-host:6379

--- Cache Configuration ---

CACHE_ENABLED=true
CACHE_TTL_SECONDS=86400
IN_MEMORY_CACHE_MAX_SIZE=52428800

--- Fetcher Configuration ---

REQ_TIMEOUT_MS=5000
HTML_PAYLOAD_LIMIT=250000
ICON_PAYLOAD_LIMIT=2097152

CUSTOM_USER_AGENT=Your Custom User Agent

--- Authentication & Limits (Case-Sensitive Keys) ---

API Keys (e.g., AUTHN0, AUTHN1, ...)

AUTHN0=secret_key_for_client_0
AUTHN1=a_different_key_123

Limits for API Keys (e.g., LIMIT0, LIMIT1, ...)

Key 0: 10 RPS, 500 RPM

LIMIT0=rps:10,rpm:500

Key 1: 2000 RPH

LIMIT1=rph:2000

--- Anonymous Limits ---

Global anonymous limit: 1 RPS, 60 RPM

LIMITA=rps:1,rpm:60

Per-IP anonymous limit: 30 RPM

LIMITI=rpm:30
